1.title: Search for Tomorrow
1.plot: Emily shares her disapproval of how the family is handling the situation with Adrien , to her cousin Junior. - Meanwhile Adrien is on the run for murder, he found himself dreaming about the very person he supposedly killed; Valentino DiMarco.

2.title: Search for Tomorrow II
2.plot: Trey can't let go of Elliott - And not ready to talk about him with anyone. - A beautiful woman appears; and claiming to be John Jasper Geary's long-lost daughter, and wants what hers. - The Gearys say their final goodbye to John Jasper Geary.

3.title: Search for Tomorrow III
3.plot: Adrien remembers something from his past. - Trey vows to protect Adrien from the DiMarco.

4.title: Search for Tomorrow IV
4.plot: The Geary family takes drastically measure to protect their love ones from the DiMarco family. - Damien opens up to his cousin Thadzio about his abuse relationship with his older brother Christian DiMarco. - Semaj agrees to move back to the Geary's Mansion for the sake of the family.

1.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part I
1.plot: A thrilling roller coaster-life of an American family dynasty. BAD News: Semaj Geary gets some bad news from his doctor, while Adrien gets a surprise visit from his uncle, and learn a shocking discovery.

2.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part II
2.plot: The Homecoming: Anastasia wants to help her brother with his health issue, but Semaj is feeling overwhelmed, and pushing everyone away. Meanwhile Giorgio DiMarco visited Adrien in jail, and wants answers.

3.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part III
3.plot: Marco finds Adrien's diary, and learns a shocking secret about the family. Semaj afraid for his cousin's life, and shares his concern with Candy and Ahton. Anastasia opening up to Benjamin about something from her past.

4.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part IV
4.plot: Tajh'Lih surprises Candy with a special gift, while she questions his where about the night before. Jennifer opens up about her marriage to Anastasia, at the same time Anastasia is receiving mysterious phone calls. Noah and Marco meet for the first time. Another deadly secret is unveil from Adrien's diary.

5.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part V
5.plot: Marco visited Adrien in Jail. Semaj learns that his sister Anastasia wants to work at The House of Fleur de Mai. Anastasia shares some news with Marco.

6.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part VI
6.plot: Semaj Geary, the leading man behind The House of Fleur de Mai new clothing line, GEO, is doing a photo shoot for GSM. John Jasper Geary and his man David, want to do some damage control to keep him out of the headlines. Noah and Marco are getting closer.

7.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part VII
7.plot: Noah and Marco are getting closer. Tajh'Lih opens up about his mother. The Crane's household isn't as peachy as it seem.

8.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part VIII
8.plot: Semaj talks to a psychiatrist. Anastasia bails out Christina Delmedico Geary Diago DiMarco resigns from the House of Fleur de Mai.

9.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part IX
9.plot: Ashley shares some news with Tajh'Lih regarding his sister, Christina. John Jasper Geary is going after the boys - Along with his wife Jackie. Trey asks Chandler for help.

10.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part X
10.plot: Amanda DiMarco questions Semaj about their past. John is spying on his wife Jackie. Jackie sets her eyes on Adrien's diary. Noah and Marco are getting closer.

11.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part XI
11.plot: Savannah confronted Chandler about his where about since Elliott's death. Trey reminded Chandler why he should consider taking on Adrien's case... The past show a deep relationship and secret lives of Savannah, Trey, Chandler and Elliott - how they're all connected. Tajh'Lih's careless acts may jeopardize his relationship with Marco.

12.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part XII
12.plot: Tajh'Lih visited Adrien in jail... Anastasia opens up about Semaj's medical condition with Jennifer, while Semaj under goes surgery. Jackie makes t e first move against Marco, while things heats up between Marco and Noah.

13.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part XIII
13.plot: Tajh'Lih and Semaj talk about his condition, and what he wants for the future. Noah questions Marco about his feeling for him, Philomena is jealous of Noah and Marco's friendship. Trey and Savannah had a fight, while Savannah remembers her friendship with Chandler.

14.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part XIV
14.plot: Marco comes out to someone from the Geary Family. Ethan got some exciting news. Trey visited the Welch family, and share some news about Elliott.

15.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part XV
15.plot: Tajh'lih and Candy's secret exposed! Christina and Tajh meet for the first time. Marco comes out to Noah, and they had a huge fight.

16.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part XVI
16.plot: Marco left town and returns to Europe, leaving Noah devastated with the news. Edwin and Kimberly have a huge fight over the children, and Noah overheard some disturbing news about his older brother Alexander. Marco Nathaniel Geary returns to Genevieve with a dark secret.

17.title: Chapter III: Aquarius Part XVII
17.plot: Jackie passes Adrien a visit before his bail hearing. Marco is working with a member of the Geary family, but quickly learned that he was being using, and what he does next is everything. Jackie, Nathan, Alistairs, Ashley Geary along with Oliver Douglas get some surprising news.

1.title: Fall & Winter - Part I
1.plot: Marco Geary explores his cousin Adrien Geary's diary, and learns some shocking secrets regarding Adrien's past. -Adrien's relationship with Benjamin Leblanc goes deeper than anyone ever known. -Valentino DiMarco is worrying that Adrien's life.

2.title: Fall & Winter - Part II
2.plot: Marco Geary explores his cousin Adrien Geary's diary, and learns some shocking secrets regarding Adrien's past. -Valentino's plan to stay from away Adrien isn't going as planned. -Adrien meets Ahton, and thanks him for saving his life, while Amanda DiMarco questioned her cousin Valentino about saving Adrien's life, and bringing him to the hospital. -Jackie wants Adrien to leave town.

3.title: Fall & Winter - Part III
3.plot: Marco Geary explores his cousin Adrien Geary's diary, and learns some shocking secrets regarding Adrien's past. -Valentino's plan to stay from away Adrien isn't going as planned. -Adrien opening about his relationship with Benjamin to Ahton, and vows to make things right, and come clean to everyone. -Jackie and Adrien have a huge fight, with Jackie ending up in the hospital.

4.title: Fall & Winter - Part IV
4.plot: Marco Geary explores his cousin Adrien Geary's diary, and learns some shocking secrets regarding Adrien's past. -Adrien learns about Jackie's pregnancy, and the death of the unborn child. -Benjamin is ordered to watch after Adrien, by Adrien's grand father John Jasper Geary - while the Geary family try to find the best way to deal with the Adrien and Jackie situation.

5.title: Fall & Winter - Part V
5.plot: Marco Geary explores his cousin Adrien Geary's diary, and learns some shocking secrets regarding Adrien's past. -Valentino wants to see Adrien, but Amanda will do anything to protect her cousin. -Jackie and Adrien must come to an understand. -Marco comes face to face with Benjamin, will he keeps quiet about the past or will he tells the family.

6.title: Fall & Winter - Part VI
6.plot: When does a boy become a man? That's the question Marco Geary finds himself struggle with throughout this season of La Fleur de Mai; as the drama heats up this Summer. -Noah is stunned by Marco's attitude toward him. -Isabella questions her step-grandmother, Jackie, about the mysterious Geary woman. -Pascal offers Marco some friendly advice. -Marco is showing signs of leadership within the Geary family.

7.title: Fall & Winter - Part VII
7.plot: When does a boy become a man? That's the question Marco Geary finds himself struggle with throughout this season of La Fleur de Mai; as the drama heats up this Summer. -Noah wants a friendship with Marco, but Marco is determined control their relationship. -Isabella concerns about Julien's feelings toward Marco. -Marco has a job interview with a top executive of La Fleur de Mai Estate. -Marco reconnects with an old friend.

8.title: Fall & Winter - Part VIII
8.plot: When does a boy become a man? That's the question Marco Geary finds himself struggle with throughout this season of La Fleur de Mai; as the drama heats up this Summer. -A darker side of Marco comes out as he tries to get control of his life and manages those around him. -Julien tries to reconnect with Marco. -Caroline Sheldon shares a dark family secret with her grandson Marco Geary. -Marco found the perfect job for Jackie.

9.title: S4.E9 Fall & Winter - Part IX
9.plot: When does a boy become a man? That's the question Marco Geary finds himself struggle with throughout this season of La Fleur de Mai; as the drama heats up this Summer. -Julien wants something more with Marco. -Jackie orders Edwin to do whatever it takes to find her dead husband. -Marco is determine to his friendship with Julien as that, just FRIEND .

10.title: Fall & Winter - Part X
10.plot: When does a boy become a man? That's the question Marco Geary finds himself struggle with throughout this season of La Fleur de Mai; as the drama heats up this Summer. -Marco Geary is making waves at The House of Fleur de Mai -Noah finds himself moving toward Marco more and more every moment. -Jackie got the votes she needs to move forward with her plan. -Marco starting asking questions about Semaj's vacationing.

11.title: Fall & Winter - Part XI
11.plot: -Marco Geary is really taking his job serious at The House of Fleur de Mai. -Julien makes his feelings very clear to Marco... -Isabella as Cassandra out. - Ashley shares her concerns regarding Jackie with Isabella. -Trey reaches out to Chandler, and Joey joins Chandler in Genevieve.

12.title: Fall & Winter - Part XII
12.plot: -Marco Geary is really taking his job serious at The House of Fleur de Mai. -Noah crashes Marco's dinner... -Julien and Sam come face to face. - Nathan Geary shows his true colors. -Someone's life will change forever.

13.title: Fall & Winter - Part XIII
13.plot: -Marco Geary is really taking his job serious at The House of Fleur de Mai. Noah crashes Marco's dinner. Nathan and his men are racing against times to stop Allain's execution. Marco sets his plan in motion, and there's no turning back on this one. -Jackie pays Christina a visit.

14.title: Fall & Winter - Part XIV
14.plot: Nathan learns a shocking secret about his daughter. Amanda has some news for Pascal. Marco gets his first major assignment. The police question Cassandra about her attacker.

15.title: Fall & Winter - Part 15
15.plot: The House of Fleur de Mai releases a new collection. Marco and Pascal have a fight, and Marco's job is on the line. Ashley questioned Penelope about a mystery girl.

imdb.plot outline: Big things are happening in the small city of Genevieve. As a small fashion house known as, "La Fleur de Mai" starts to bloom. It makes enemies with the notorious DiMarco family. As this rivalry turns more scandalous, everyone involved in the feud must cope with the wilting threat of HIV/AIDS and the three men who must face it.
